   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Only personnel trained and certified by Reality are authorized to
work on and with this Reality. Reality certified personnel must have
a valid 2-year certificate from Reality.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The validity and scope of the certificate should also be checked
by the Customer with their local <xref conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
               class="- topic/xref "/> before any installation, commissioning, service or maintenance
is performed by the personnel.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">No responsibility or liability is assumed by Reality if work on or
with this Reality is performed by non-certified personnel.</p>
